curam.common.util.xml.dom

Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.common.util.xml.dom.Content
      • curam.common.util.xml.dom.Element
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DomWrapper

    public class Element
extends Content
    An Element defines an XML element. An element can have declared namespaces, attributes, child nodes and textual content. This implementation wraps a dom4j Element.
